{"tid":1741202,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【轉會情報】熱刺或引入桑馬達","createTime":"2019-11-20T08:35:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T14:10:45.000Z","uid":214972,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a5a94333f7398a12cf9f892b72e2cf5164df428a","tid":1741202,"uid":214972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:35:51.000Z","msg":"車路士中場桑馬達在英超大戰曼聯中，再一次被領隊摩連奴放在後備，沒有出場，這位西班牙國腳盛傳獲馬德里體育會青睞。不過，倫敦球會的熱刺也對桑馬達有興趣，希望以他取代有機會離隊的加里夫巴利。由於早前搶購韋利安失敗，而洽購羅馬翼鋒拉美拿也只在磋商階段，未有落實，故熱刺極希望盡快找到合適人選，為陣容補強。25歲的桑馬達周薪超過95,000鎊（約114萬港元），是馬體會難以支付的薪金，故熱刺方面有機會在爭奪戰中勝出。<br />\n<br />\n2013-08-27 即時體育 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20130827/51676736\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20130827%2F51676736&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLAmr2u8Aa6r9E8tiWteYAjM%3D&h=2bea9d4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20130827%2F51676736&h=a4ff1b10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20130827/51676736</a>"},{"pid":"63ec7dff2bb380d0957bb4d328bd6e70c02a71a6","tid":1741202,"uid":301523,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:10:02.000Z","msg":"竟然有post埋日期"},{"pid":"1a5417a77dcc0436d0aac8a093e53ab5aa225b56","tid":1741202,"uid":66536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:06:43.000Z","msg":"應該會買契仔馬迪"},{"pid":"43cbd9cf8f6180b8ee0d02f1fe21dc3b6bf7a96a","tid":1741202,"uid":60695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fc7d28c982a5ba544dc9e33d380aee9dd3f5c7","tid":1741202,"uid":111019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:10:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}